00053 //  NOTE that the 0xFFFF of 0xFF entries at the end of some tables below are
00054 //  not properly list terminators, but are actually the printable definitions
00055 //  of values that are legitimately found on the PCI bus.  The size
00056 //  definitions should be used for loop control when the table is searched.
00057
